Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.68,0:00:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Kids! Kids, take a look at today's prophet!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.82,0:00:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no! No more prophets! Enough of that shit!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.69,0:00:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh no!\N- What is it?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.27,0:00:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- Gather around, y'all...\N- No. Harry, you not gonna wanna see this.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.95,0:00:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ministry of magic sentences Sirius Black\Nto Death by way of the Dementor's kiss.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.68,0:00:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Bogus! Mondo bummer!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.23,0:00:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not the worst of it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.97,0:00:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone read the next few sentences?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.44,0:00:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,To administer the kiss, a force of 1000\Ndementors will be sent to Hogwarts, ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.78,0:00:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...where after carrying out the execution,\Nthey will remain a new permanent security force...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.49,0:00:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...under the direct control of\NHeadmaster Dolores Umbridge.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.95,0:00:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the absolute worst!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.56,0:00:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Umbridge done turn the school into a prison!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.85,0:00:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over. She won.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.19,0:00:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention all Hogwarts students:
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.80,0:00:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Umbridge.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.19,0:00:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Will all those nasty little first years\Nwho have dention this evening, ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.99,0:00:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...please report immediately to the owlery.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.02,0:01:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Your duties this evening will include\Nrestocking the bird seeds supply, ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.08,0:01:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...getting eggs from the meanest, angriest owls...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.86,0:01:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...and scrubbing bird shit off the floor.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.13,0:01:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring your toothbrushes.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.57,0:01:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Failure to attend detention will reserve in\Nsome serious though love consequences.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.76,0:01:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So get moving everyone!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.00,0:01:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone except for the famous Harry Potter.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.52,0:01:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Potter, your detention will be held with me tonight.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.72,0:01:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So please report to my office immediately!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.05,0:01:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Alone.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.87,0:01:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, that's all. Bye! Have fun!\N[laughing]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.51,0:01:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Harry, I don't like the sound of this.\NWhy does she wanna meet you alone?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.12,0:01:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, why don't you have to clean up\Nbird shit like the rest of us?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.62,0:01:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I mean what if she does\Nsomething horrible to you?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.03,0:01:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, she can't, she's a teacher.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.03,0:01:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, maybe I can talk to her about Sirius.\NYou can't just sent someone to death who is innocent.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.91,0:01:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't think she cares if he's innocent or not.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.07,0:01:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,She has to. Any sane, reasonable person would.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.37,0:02:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides I don't know what I'll do if I won't be able to hug\Nor kiss Sirius Black, my best adult friend, ever again.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.77,0:02:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to try!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.67,0:02:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see you, guys.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.86,0:02:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- Good luck!\N- Be carefull!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.23,0:02:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[Snape is singing "Hedwig's theme" drunk]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.35,0:02:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Potter! Potter!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.07,0:02:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. The the one I wanted to see. Sit down, dude!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.29,0:02:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, I ... I gotta go to Umbridge's office.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.09,0:02:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now? Can't you wait?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.47,0:02:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ah, there's a...\N- Harry Potter, I'm a teacher. You have to listen to me!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.71,0:02:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You.. you have to listen to me or I'll expel you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.21,0:02:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll expel you now!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.71,0:02:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit down!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.62,0:02:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Want a beer?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.56,0:02:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, no. That's okay!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.81,0:02:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! Come on! Man, don't\Nmake me be the only one drinking!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.26,0:02:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.01,0:02:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, those are mine!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.55,0:02:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Potter, ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.39,0:02:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[babbeling]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.20,0:02:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I haaafeadelemon.\N[more babbeling]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.37,0:02:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a dilemma.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.00,0:02:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your dilemma?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.92,0:03:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I promised Dumbledore, that I'll protect the school.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.25,0:03:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But the thing is, Potter:
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.11,0:03:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.88,0:03:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate you so much!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.53,0:03:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.39,0:03:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I hate you too, Snape.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.84,0:03:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not fair, really. 'Cause -- it's your dad is who I hated.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.88,0:03:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was in love with your mum.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.17,0:03:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But I had a butt trumpet.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.48,0:03:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My butt went -- boop, boop. Boop, boop. Boop, boop.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.07,0:03:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And she choose him over me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.68,0:03:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- You know how that is?\N- I don't know what your're talking...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.70,0:03:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what pisses me off! I mean, really...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.96,0:03:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...[beep] pisses me off, ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.23,0:03:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...is that I was there for her, you know?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.76,0:03:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Like when she needed someone, I was there.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.35,0:03:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Waiting like a tool.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.11,0:03:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Saying: are we gonna snog now? No? Okay. Now?\NWhat about now? Always! Always forever, like a tool.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.18,0:03:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And just once...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.31,0:03:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one time...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.12,0:04:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to take your mum's...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.27,0:04:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,...boobies...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.51,0:04:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...and put them on my face.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.64,0:04:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And go... BURRRRRRRRRRrrrrr.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.18,0:04:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're talking about. I...I don't\Nwanna say any sayings. I'm just gonna let you pass out here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.25,0:04:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Potter! What I'm trying to say is that I'm torn up.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.21,0:04:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And if... if you go in there, you gonna be in big trouble!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.68,0:04:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever, Snape.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.09,0:04:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Butt trumpet!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.28,0:04:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, forget you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.78,0:04:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Umbridge?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.16,0:04:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me, HP. You asked me to come here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.32,0:04:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna talk to you about something.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.41,0:04:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.89,0:04:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hello, boy!\N- Oh, hi!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.62,0:04:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupefy!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.90,0:04:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Argh!
